textBeforeTable: The Precision ProValu Great Crate Single Door Dog Crate with FREE Pad gives you convenient access to your pet and a comfortable, safe place for him to stay. This wire cage features easy latches and rounded corners, and a plastic tray at the bottom that's easy to clean. The cage is electro-coated in black. It comes in a variety of sizes and assembled, so it's ready to set up and use!   Description Divider Panel What's Not Included Dog crate, faux sheepskin pad What's Included Several sizes available Rust-resistant finish FREE leak-proof ABS plastic pan included
